### OpenStack Database Backup

ALERT OpenstackDatabaseBackupAge
  IF (time()-backup_last_success)/60/60 >= 24
  FOR 3m
  LABELS {
    tier = "openstack",
    service = "backup",
    severity = "warning",
    context = "backupage",
    dashboard = "database-replication"
  }
  ANNOTATIONS {
    summary = "Database Backup too old",
    description = "The last successful database backup is {{ $value }} hours old."
  }
